column5:
added ability to disable/re-enable tooltips via the API

$().tooltipster('disable');
$(...).tooltipster('enable');

added option for functionReady() - fires when tooltip contents have been added to DOM

$(...).tooltipster({
    functionReady: function(origin, tooltipster) {
        ...
    }
});

origin = element tooltip originates from
tooltipster = tooltip itself
